from scipy.fftpack import fft, fftfreq


semitransformada = ImagenRGBcv2.copy()
semitransformada = np.vectorize(complex)(semitransformada, np.zeros_like(semitransformada))
transformada = np.vectorize(complex)(semitransformada, np.zeros_like(semitransformada))

for i in range(len(ImagenRGBcv2[:,1])):
    f = ImagenRGBcv2[i,:]
    semitransformada[i,:] = fft(f)


for i in range(len(ImagenRGBcv2[1,:])):
    f = semitransformada[:,i]
    transformada[:,i] = fft(f)
In [ ]:
for i in range(len(transformada[:,1])):
    for j in range(len(transformada[1,:])):
        transformada[i,j]= np.abs(semitransformada[i,j])
